    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg text-center sm:text-start">
        <p>
          Currently working as a Software Engineer at{" "}
        <a href="https://academiauniversitaria.paraninfo.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 block my-1 sm:inline">
          Academia Universitaria Paraninfo
        </a>
        </p>
        <p>
          Also a Data Science student at{" "}
        <a href="https://www.iu.org/en-za/bachelor/data-science/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 block my-1 sm:inline">
          Int. University of Applied Sciences (<b>IU</b>)
        </a>
        </p>
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 w-full flex justify-around sm:mt-8 sm:justify-normal">
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:ignaciog00@gmail.com?subject=Let's%20connect&body=Hi,%20I%20came%20here%20from%20your%20personal%20site." target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
